.TH AI-PLAYBOOK-LIST 1 "" "ai-playbook" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ai\-playbook\-list \- List every saved playbook
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBai\-playbook\fR list [\-\-format human|fuzzy\-data\-source|json]
.SH DESCRIPTION
list enumerates the full store index in the requested format. The human
format's LAST RUN column shows each playbook's last journaled run in the
current project: ✓ or ✗ plus the run's total elapsed time, a bare ✗ for a
run interrupted mid\-flight, or – when never run.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<fmt>\fR
output format: human|fuzzy\-data\-source|json
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
ai\-playbook list
.fi
.PP
.nf
ai\-playbook list \-\-format json
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBai\-playbook\fR(1)
